metadata.name: LittleBoo #1
metadata.description:
‘LittleBoos’ aim to be a well recognised creative brand in the industries of Children’s Books, Indie Kiddie Comics and Children focussed E-commerce.
This collection is a mix of hand-drawn original artwork and random generative process.
    
For the benefits to holders, both short and long term, refer to our articles, socials and website.
    
www.littleboos.com
